%% Design brief (per mermaid-arc-skills 0. inference + DESIGN.md "Text-first, preview-compatible source" vision):
%% flowchart TD + subgraph COMPATIBLE approximation of three-layer closed loop.
%% This is the CANONICAL form for any architecture / arc / layered view that will live inside Markdown source
%% (research papers, design logs, Obsidian, GitHub READMEs, Typora etc.).
%% It avoids ALL architecture-beta lexer errors with <br/>, Chinese, arrows in Mermaid 11.x / Typora / Obsidian / GitHub.
%% Preserves: core as sovereign foundation (strong IKB), three layers as groups, ritual closed-loop edges (explicit labels),
%% single accent, restrained Swiss + warm paper tokens, "越大越细，越小越粗", hairline, geometry focus.
%% 
%% For full-featured beautiful SVG (production PPT/PDF/LaTeX): take the beta version from three-layer-closed-loop.mmd
%% and feed to pretty-mermaid / mermaid-rs-renderer / latest cli. Do NOT use beta as the source block.
%% 
%% Dials: Complexity 5 (layered system), Density 5 (practices + rituals), Restraint 9 (single IKB, hairline, no rainbow).
%% Visual language: sovereign ritual on warm paper; Swiss typography; core as data sovereign foundation;
%% layers as groups; ritual edges as design interventions; dashed data主权 from base.
%% Variation: Use this for system view in recurring three-layer contexts (pair with mindmap philosophy variant).
%% Follows mermaid-arc-skills + guizang locked mode + DESIGN.md recurring variation + compatibility-first rule.
flowchart TD
    subgraph 物质层 ["物质层 · Money"]
        daily[日均成本计算]
        dates[buyDate vs startDate 分离]
        sell[卖出结算闭环]
    end

    subgraph 思维层 ["思维层 · Knowledge"]
        notes[Markdown-native 笔记]
        meta[使用元数据关联]
        zettlr[Zettlr 桌面协同]
    end

    subgraph 情感层 ["情感层 · Sentiment"]
        trigger[仅里程碑触发]
        guide[购入引导 + 卖出告别]
        peak[情感峰值补偿]
    end

    subgraph 核心 [".md 数据主权 / Local-first / 被动 AI / 完整归档"]
        local[Local-first]
        passive[被动 AI]
        archive[完整归档]
    end

    %% Ritual closed loop flows
    daily -->|持有日常| dates
    dates -->|触发卖出| sell
    sell -->|卖出告别仪式| 核心
    notes -->|闪念| meta
    meta -->|被动重组| zettlr
    zettlr -->|导出调用| 核心
    trigger -->|里程碑触发| guide
    guide -->|情感仪式| peak
    peak -->|峰值补偿归档| 核心

    核心 -.->|"数据主权"| 物质层
    核心 -.->|"数据主权"| 思维层
    核心 -.->|"数据主权"| 情感层

    classDef coreCore fill:#f5f0eb,stroke:#002FA7,stroke-width:2px,color:#1B365D
    classDef layerGroup fill:#f0f0ee,stroke:#a8a29e,color:#44403c
    class 核心 coreCore
    class 物质层,思维层,情感层 layerGroup
